can not contain words “Arian”, “AMU”, “Tarumian”, be they written in Latin and/or Armenian
characters or with any script system;
in case changed fonts are disseminated or used there should be a clear indication that
they derive from the Arian AMU fonts;
The Fonts or items created on the basis of the Fonts may not be an object of sale.
